title: Two Sum
description: Given an array of integers nums and an integer target, return indices of the two numbers such that they add up to target. Each input would have exactly one solution, and you may not use the same element twice. Return the indices in sorted order separated by space.
input_format: The first line contains integers separated by space (nums). The second line contains the target integer.
output_format: Two indices separated by space, in non-decreasing order.
